{
  "chapter": "090",
  "title": "魏豹彭越列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "周市立咎",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span>是故<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>之一。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏咎</span>，旧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>时封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宁陵君</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>迁为平民。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>起兵称王后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>前往投奔他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">陈王（陈胜）</span>派<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>去攻取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>，众人想共同<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>昏乱，忠<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>才显现。如今<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，从道义上讲必<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王后裔才行。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>各派<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>五十乘，要<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周市\">市（周市）</span>辞不受，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏咎</span>。往返五次，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">陈王（陈胜）</span>才派人<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "魏咎自烧",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈胜\">陈王（陈胜）</span>，便进<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王便派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>出去向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>求救。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项它</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田巴</span>率<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周市\">市（周市）</span>救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>便<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>等人的军队，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>为他的百姓约定<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span>。约定后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">烧</span>而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "魏豹立为魏王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>，让他再去攻取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀城</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>率精<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>入关。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉元年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，想占有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁地</span>，便把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>迁至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>，都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">西魏</span>王。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "魏豹叛汉",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王还<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三秦</span>，渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临晋</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>以国归附，便随从<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，退至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>请求回国看望病亲，到国后就切断<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河津</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，正东忧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，来不及<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>说：\"你温言去劝说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span>，能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>他，我以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>封你。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>劝说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>辞谢说：\"人生一世，如〘※白驹过隙〙。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王傲慢侮人，辱骂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>如骂奴仆，无上下<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼节</span>，我不忍再见他。\" 于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>，传送至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>之国为郡。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">守</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>得急，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "彭越聚众",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>人，字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">仲（彭越）</span>。常在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜野泽</span>中打渔，做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群盗</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>起事，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少年</span>有人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>说：\"诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪桀</span>都在<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>起来<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">仲（彭越）</span>可以来效仿。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>说：\"两龙正在争斗，暂且等等。\""
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "治众立威",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">岁馀（时长）</span>，泽间<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少年</span>相聚<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>，去投奔<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，说：\"请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">仲（彭越）</span>做头领。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>辞谢说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不愿和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸君</span>共事。\" 少年强请，才答应。约定次日日出会合，迟到者<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>。次日日出，有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>迟到，最晚的到了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日中</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>辞谢说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>老了，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸君</span>强让我做头领。如今约定时间而迟到者众多，不能都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>最后到的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。\" 令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校长</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>他。众人都笑说：\"何至于如此？以后不敢。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>便拉出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了，设坛祭祀，号令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">徒属</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">徒属</span>都大惊，畏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>，无人敢仰视。于是行动<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span>地，收<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>散卒，得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "彭越归汉",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">沛公（刘邦）</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>北面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>助他。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>未<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">沛公（刘邦）</span>率<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>西进。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>也带其众居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜野</span>中，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">收</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的散卒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>入关，[王<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，还归，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>众<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀人</span>无所归属。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉元年秋</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>，派人赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，使他<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阴</span>以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧公角</span>率<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉王二年春</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>率其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万馀人</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">外黄</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭（彭越）</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">收</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀城</span>，想急〖○立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王后代。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">西魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>也是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>的从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>，真正的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王后代。\" 便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，独领其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁地</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "游兵助汉",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>退西归，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span>失其所<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>城邑，独率其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>北居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河上</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉王三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>常往来为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>作游<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，切断其后路<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粮</span>道于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁地</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉四年冬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王相持于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">外黄</span>十七城。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>闻之，便派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹咎</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">守</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>，自己东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">收</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>所<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>城邑，都重归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>率其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穀城</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉五年秋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳夏</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>附近<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀城</span>，得<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">穀</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万</span>斛，以供<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王食用。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "彭越为梁王",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，派使召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>合力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地初<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span>，还怕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，不能离开。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">固陵</span>。便对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>不跟随，怎么办？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>之立，非<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：刘邦\">君王（刘邦）</span>本意，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>心中不安。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>本<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁地</span>，功多，当初<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：刘邦\">君王（刘邦）</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span>之故，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>无后，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>也想[王，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：刘邦\">君王（刘邦）</span>没有早〖◈定。与这两国相约：若[胜<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>以北至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穀城</span>，都[王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭（彭越）</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>以东到海，给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>家在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，他的意思是想再得故邑。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：刘邦\">君王（刘邦）</span>能舍出此地许<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>今日即可招致；若不能，事情难料。\" 于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王派使者到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>处，按<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>之策。使者到，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>便尽引<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>会合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垓下</span>，便<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>。春，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王，都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "朝见长安",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，朝见于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>、<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，都来朝<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "彭越族灭",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年秋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>亲自前往<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>之，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，征<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王称病，派将率<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>怒，派人责备<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王恐，想亲往谢罪。他的将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扈辄</span>说：\"王当初不去，被责备才去，去必被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">禽</span>。不如起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王不听，仍称病。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王怒其<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span>，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>他。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，告<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扈辄</span>谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>。于是上派人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">掩</span>袭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王未觉察，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">捕</span>获<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>审治反形已具，请依法论处。上<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>他为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>，流放到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">青衣</span>。西行至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，遇<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>来，要去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>，路上见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>哭诉，自言无罪，愿处故乡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>答应，一同东去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>对上说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>，如今〖[徙他到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>，这是自留祸患，不如便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>之。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妾</span>谨将他带来。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>让他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>再谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恬开</span>奏请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>之。上允准，便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">夷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗族</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>虽然出身卑贱，然而已能席卷<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，南面称孤，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">喋</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">血</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">乘</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span>，声名日盛。心怀<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">畔</span>逆之意，等到<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>后，不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>，身受<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">戮</span>，为什么？中等以上才能之人尚且羞于这种行为，何况是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>呢！他们没别的原因，智略过人，只患身不能保。得到一寸之<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">柄</span>，就云蒸龙变，想有所作为以施展其志，所以被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">幽</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>也不推辞。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏咎</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>，因时而[王。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>后附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，其国遂<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">仲（彭越）</span>起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>，归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">外黄</span>。 往来声援，再续军<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粮</span>。 征<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>不应，〖[菹醢何伤。"
    }
